      <title>工党为建造更多住房而修改规划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/labour-fleshes-out-planning-changes-in-bid-to-build-more-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国副首相安格拉·雷纳 (Angela Rayner) 表示，英国新政府将让地方议会更容易在绿化带上建设住房并恢复强制性的当地住房目标，她进一步充实了工党在本届议会期间每年提供 30 万套新住房的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/labour-fleshes-out-planning-changes-in-bid-to-build-more-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市审计长兰德宣布竞选市长，与亚当斯竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/nyc-comptroller-lander-announces-bid-for-mayor-against-adams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市审计长布拉德·兰德加入了越来越多的候选人名单，他们计划在明年的民主党初选中挑战市长埃里克·亚当斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/nyc-comptroller-lander-announces-bid-for-mayor-against-adams</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
